Package org.opennars.operator

Class Operator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opennars.language.Term
      • org.opennars.operator.Operator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable, Comparable<AbstractTerm>, AbstractTerm, Plugin
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Abbreviation.Abbreviate, Anticipate, Believe, Consider, Doubt, Evaluate, Feel, FunctionOperator, Hesitate, Name, NullOperator, Register, Remind, Want, Wonder
    public abstract class Operator
extends Term
implements Plugin
    An individual operator that can be execute by the system, which can be either inside NARS or outside it, in another system or device.

    This is the only file to modify when registering a new operator into NARS.
